The paper proposes a method for solving the problem of Ranking under Team Context (RTC) on datasets without a priori. This problem is related to data management and information retrieval, which suggests that the paper may belong to the cs.DB and cs.IR sub-categories. The proposed method involves constructing window queries and pre-pruning tuples, which are techniques commonly used in artificial intelligence and data structures, respectively. Therefore, the paper may also belong to the cs.AI and cs.DS sub-categories. Finally, the paper evaluates its algorithm's performance, which is a common practice in machine learning and computational statistics, suggesting that it may also belong to the cs.LG sub-category.
